Summary
Product designer, engineer, and entrepreneur specializing in sustainable innovation. Co-founded a startup converting recycled medical-waste plastic into high-performance composite products—developing 70+ designs that achieved 65% weight reduction while maintaining structural integrity. Bring expertise in advanced composites, parametric design (Rhino/Grasshopper), and end-to-end operations from supply chain management to cross-functional team leadership. Passionate about proving environmental innovation and product excellence aren’t mutually exclusive.

